	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There is definitely 5V FlashROMs available in PLCC (as well as EEPROMs, I guess), and they'll fit the cart case with some sockets, but you'll need to make your own PCB to plug them in, because I doubt any PLCC to DIP adaptator can fit the case.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
