		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Bregalad wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">because I doubt any PLCC to DIP adaptator can fit the case.</div>
<br />
<br />They definitely won't.  I had previously considered producing my own insanely low-profile PLCC to DIP adapters (that would also wire the ROM to a MaskROM pinout).  But I realized as nifty as it the idea is, it's unlikely to be popular enough to make up for the setup cost of the PCB layout.

		

		</td>
